HEADWORD: Pericope
<hw>Pe*ric"o*pe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., section
of a book, Gr. <?/; <grk>peri`</grk> around + <?/ to cut.]</ety> <def>A
